		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello,
<br />
<br />I've googled the hell out of this game and all I find is people saying they can't get the save to work on multicarts like the everdrive or single pcb donors. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_cry.gif" alt=":cry:" title="Crying or Very sad" />  That or if I do find postings about a working copy it's only from people looking to SELL the english transated copy of the game. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_rolleyes.gif" alt=":roll:" title="Rolling Eyes" />
<br />
<br /> The most I've been able to gather is there is an issue with the SRAM saving. One person even mentioned that it might be cause it uses more than 8k to save which 8k is the norm on most common sports title donors from my experience. Is it probable that replacing the 8k sram with 32k sram would fix this issue or prehaps it's a bigger issue than that?
<br />
<br />Anyhow I really look forward to finding out how to make the translated english version of King Colossus work cause I will spread the info freely on the net so the next person or persons don't have to go crazy looking for info to get this game working correctly on real hardware. Any and all help is greatly appricated and will be sure to get echoed in the futrure.
<br />
<br />Thanks!

		

		</td>
